text: Kwaku Boateng may refer to: * Kwaku Boateng (athlete) (born 1974), Canadian high jumper * Kwaku Boateng (politician) (died 2006), cabinet minister in Ghana in the early 1960s * Kwaku Boateng (Canadian football) (born 1995), Canadian football player * Kwaku Agyenim Boateng (born 1972), Ghanaian politician
title: Kwaku Boateng
